headline: 3 Stocks That Cut You a Check Each Month
summary: Realty Income is a net-lease giant with a high yield and a 30-year dividend history.  Agree Realty is a smaller net-lease REIT focused on growth and has increased its dividend for a decade.  LTC Properties is a healthcare REIT that is leaning into a key growth platform.
